                        </a></div></div><ol class="sense_single" htag="ol"><li class="sense" hclass="sense" id="alger_sng_1" htag="li"><span class="sensetop" hclass="sensetop" htag="span"><span class="def" htag="span" hclass="def">(1834-99) a US author of more than 100 books for boys. Most were about poor boys who became rich and successful by their hard work and good behaviour. Readers believed that these ‘rags-to-riches’ stories illustrated the opportunities for success in America.</span></span>    <div id="ring-links-box">
